edge: The film's music was composed by Singer and Composer Sukhwinder Singh.
'Jab Tak Hai Dum' song from the movie is sung by Sukhwinder Singh.
'Shabad Gurbani' song from the movie is sung by Sukhwinder Singh.
'Is Pal Ki Soch' song from the movie is sung by Harshdeep Kaur.
'More Haji Piya' song from the movie is sung by Amjad Farid Sabri.
'Barsan Lagi' song from the movie is sung by Sneha Pant.
